parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I’m not ready yet. I need a nice suit before I dare have dinner with the commissioner.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.I’m not ready yet. I should bring some wine and not show up empty handed.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I’ve got the wine, and I’ve got a nice suit… I’m ready.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Actually, I left it at my home just across the way. I’ll be right back.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.I forgot to pick up an aloe plant.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.This vase is made of metal. I’m not strong enough to break it open.");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.It’s the damn operation… The mansion belongs to the state…");

$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoEx.Let her know I didn’t mean for this to happen.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe^.Well, I guess that’s one way to handle things…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoDe^.I hope Kimberly isn’t too pissed at me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.You don’t mean that. You’d love to see me fall from grace.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnOp.Not at the expense of my work.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MeAnEx.I’m still a part of this case, 1Hero. And you still work for me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFlDe.And I look forward to more… private meetings.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.This vase is made of metal. I’m not strong enough to break it open.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I’ll see if I can figure out where she is.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.I’m here to meet with the commissioner.");
